{"data":[{"name":"75:1","price":"1. Aku bersumpah dengan hari Kiamat,","arabic":"لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5552,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:2","price":"2. Dan aku bersumpah demi jiwa yang selalu menyesali (dirinya sendiri).","arabic":"وَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5553,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:3","price":"3. Apakah manusia mengira, bahwa Kami tidak akan mengumpulkan (kembali) tulang belulangnya?","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5554,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:4","price":"4. (Bahkan) Kami mampu menyusun (kembali) jari jemarinya dengan sempurna.","arabic":"بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5555,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:5","price":"5. Tetapi manusia hendak membuat maksiat terus-menerus.","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفۡجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5556,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:6","price":"6. Dia bertanya, “Kapankah hari Kiamat?”","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5557,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:7","price":"7. Maka apabila mata terbelalak (ketakutan),","arabic":"فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5558,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:8","price":"8. Dan bulan pun telah hilang cahayanya,","arabic":"وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5559,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:9","price":"9. Lalu matahari dan bulan dikumpulkan,","arabic":"وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5560,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:10","price":"10. Pada hari itu manusia berkata, “Ke mana tempat lari?”","arabic":"يَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَيۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5561,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:11","price":"11. Tidak! Tidak ada tempat berlindung!","arabic":"كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5562,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:12","price":"12. Hanya kepada Tuhanmu tempat kembali pada hari itu.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5563,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:13","price":"13. Pada hari itu diberitakan kepada manusia apa yang telah dikerjakannya dan apa yang telah dilalaikannya.","arabic":"يُنَبَّؤُاْ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5564,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:14","price":"14. Bahkan manusia menjadi saksi atas dirinya sendiri,*(880)","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفۡسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5565,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"*880). Anggota badan manusia menjadi saksi terhadap pekerjaan yang telah mereka lakukan seperti tersebut dalam Surah An-Nūr (24) ayat 24.","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:15","price":"15. Dan meskipun dia mengemukakan alasan-alasannya.","arabic":"وَلَوۡ أَلۡقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5566,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:16","price":"16. Jangan engkau (Muhammad) gerakkan lidahmu (untuk membaca Al-Qur`ān) karena hendak cepat-cepat (menguasai)nya.","arabic":"لَا تُحَرِّكۡ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعۡجَلَ بِهِۦٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5567,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:17","price":"17. Sesungguhnya Kami yang akan mengumpulkannya (di dadamu) dan membacakannya.","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا جَمۡعَهُۥ وَقُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5568,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:18","price":"18. Apabila Kami telah selesai membacakannya, maka ikutilah bacaannya itu.","arabic":"فَإِذَا قَرَأۡنَٰهُ فَٱتَّبِعۡ قُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5569,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:19","price":"19. Kemudian sesungguhnya Kami yang akan menjelaskannya.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا بَيَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5570,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:20","price":"20. Tidak! Bahkan kamu mencintai kehidupan dunia,","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُحِبُّونَ ٱلۡعَاجِلَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5571,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:21","price":"21. dan mengabaikan (kehidupan) akhirat.","arabic":"وَتَذَرُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5572,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:22","price":"22. Wajah-wajah (orang mukmin) pada hari itu berseri-seri.","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاضِرَةٌ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5573,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:23","price":"23. Memandang Tuhannya.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5574,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:24","price":"24. Dan wajah-wajah (orang kafir) pada hari itu muram,","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بَاسِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5575,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:25","price":"25. Mereka yakin bahwa akan ditimpakan kepadanya malapetaka yang sangat dahsyat.","arabic":"تَظُنُّ أَن يُفۡعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5576,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:26","price":"26. Tidak! Apabila (nyawa) telah sampai ke kerongkongan,","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلتَّرَاقِيَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5577,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:27","price":"27. Dan dikatakan (kepadanya), “Siapa yang dapat menyembuhkan?”","arabic":"وَقِيلَ مَنۡۜ رَاقٖ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5578,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:28","price":"28. Dan dia yakin bahwa itulah waktu perpisahan (dengan dunia),","arabic":"وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ ٱلۡفِرَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5579,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:29","price":"29. Dan bertaut betis (kiri) dengan betis (kanan),*(881)","arabic":"وَٱلۡتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5580,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"*881). Karena hebatnya penderitaan pada saat akan mati dan ketakutan akan meninggalkan dunia dan menghadapi akhirat.","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:30","price":"30. kepada Tuhanmulah pada hari itu kamu dihalau.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمَسَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5581,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:31","price":"31. Karena dia (dahulu) tidak mau membenarkan (Al-Qur`ān dan Rasul) dan tidak mau melaksanakan salat,","arabic":"فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5582,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:32","price":"32. tetapi justru dia mendustakan (Rasul) dan berpaling (dari kebenaran),","arabic":"وَلَٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5583,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:33","price":"33. kemudian dia pergi kepada keluarganya, dengan sombong.","arabic":"ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5584,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:34","price":"34. Celakalah kamu! Maka celakalah!","arabic":"أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5585,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:35","price":"35. Sekali lagi, celakalah kamu (manusia)! Maka celakalah!","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5586,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:36","price":"36. Apakah manusia mengira, dia akan dibiarkan begitu saja (tanpa pertanggungjawaban)?","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَن يُتۡرَكَ سُدًى","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5587,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:37","price":"37. Bukankah dia mulanya hanya setetes mani yang ditumpahkan (ke dalam rahim).","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَكُ نُطۡفَةٗ مِّن مَّنِيّٖ يُمۡنَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5588,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:38","price":"38. Kemudian (mani itu) menjadi sesuatu yang melekat, lalu Allah menciptakannya dan menyempurnakannya,","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةٗ فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5589,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:39","price":"39. lalu Dia menjadikan darinya sepasang laki-laki dan perempuan.","arabic":"فَجَعَلَ مِنۡهُ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5590,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"75:40","price":"40. Bukankah (Allah yang berbuat) demikian berkuasa (pula) menghidupkan orang mati?","arabic":"أَلَيۡسَ ذَٰلِكَ بِقَٰدِرٍ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحۡـِۧيَ ٱلۡمَوۡتَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5591,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah","Chapter Al-Qiyamah","Qiyamah","Surah Qiyamah","Chapter Qiyamah","Al Qiyamah","Surah Al Qiyamah","Chapter Al Qiyamah","Surah 75","Chapter 75","The Resurrection","القيامة"]}